Key Match Events: David Miller scored an unbeaten 59 from 51 balls to give South Africa the victory
South Africa lost four wickets in the first ten overs
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Netherlands won this fixture in the last T20 World Cup and again in the ODI version last year
Others: Marco Jansen's height made him almost unplayable on this springy pitch
Anrich Nortje's pace was hardly any easier to face
